data.description: CHARMING HOME in Lake Elsinor.  Features 4 bedroom, 2 bath with an ADDED BONUS room.  Kitchen has been remodled with Granite counter tops, back splash and cabinets.  Perfect for a first time homeowner or large family!  Spacious back yard with privacy wood fence.  Local amenities are near by, shopping centers, restaurants, schools and much more.  The park and Lake are just walking distance.  Enjoy the beautiful views of the surrounding mountains and Lake when you walk outside your front or back yard.
